snippet.title: From Dust | Launch Trailer for Xbox LIVE Arcade [NORTH AMERICA]
snippet.description:
Discover the new game of visionary director, Eric Chahi. Game critics award From Dust best strategy game at E3. 

More info at www.fromdustgame.com
